 physical improvements now.

576
00:32:01,720 --> 00:32:03,389
Her speech and writing 
 are getting better.

577
00:32:04,623 --> 00:32:07,026
Keep her an extra hour
from now on.

578
00:32:07,059 --> 00:32:08,694
