00:35:57,556 --> 00:36:01,560
"Congratulations!
Today is your day.

625
00:36:01,593 --> 00:36:04,196
"You're off to great places.

626
00:36:04,230 --> 00:36:06,332
"You're off and away.

627
00:36:06,365 --> 00:36:08,734
"You have brains in your head.

628
00:36:08,767 --> 00:36:11,537
"You have feet in your shoes.

629
00:36:11,570 --> 00:36:16,242
"You can steer yourself
any direction you choose.

630
00:36:16,275 --> 00:36:20,279
"You'll be on your way up. 
 You'll be seeing great sights.

631
00:36:20,312 --> 00:36:24,616
"You'll join the high fliers 
 who soar to high heights.

632
00:36:24,650 --> 00:36:28,354
"Wherever you fly, 
 you'll be best of the best.

633
00:36:28,387 --> 00:36:31,857
"Wherever you go, 
 you will top all the rest.

634
00:36:31,890 --> 00:36:34,793
"Oh, the places you'll go!"

