00:37:13,432 --> 00:37:15,834
Simmer down here,
you're overreacting.
I'm not Professor Higgins.

647
00:37:15,867 --> 00:37:18,570
No, you're a doctor!

648
00:37:18,604 --> 00:37:20,005
She has no experience
with life,
you should know that.

649
00:37:20,038 --> 00:37:22,708
Her therapy
is going very well.

650
00:37:22,741 --> 00:37:24,743
Dina's more important
than your little
experiment here.

651
00:37:24,776 --> 00:37:26,845
I want you to take a look
at her. She's learning,
she's reading,

652
00:37:26,878 --> 00:37:28,580
-she's happy.
