Are you not hungry?

1334
01:22:53,536 --> 01:22:54,570
Huh? (CHUCKLES)

1335
01:22:57,506 --> 01:22:58,474
What's wrong with you guys?

1336
01:23:15,358 --> 01:23:18,161
"Two cc's placebo.
No formula."

1337
01:23:18,761 --> 01:23:20,163
What the hell?

1338
01:23:26,635 --> 01:23:27,436
What's going on here?

1339
01:23:29,138 --> 01:23:32,208
They were having
secondary reactions.

1340
01:23:32,241 --> 01:23:35,078
I think the formula invaded
the limbic system,
threw off their body clocks.

1341
01:23:36,245 --> 01:23:37,380
It's like they
were burning out.

1342
01:23:37,413 --> 01:23:38,514
Burning out?

1343
01:23:38,547 --> 01:23:39,682
They weren't sleeping.

1344
01:23:39,715 --> 01:23:40,716
They hated the dark.

1345
01:23:41,517 --> 01:23:42,751
Light stimulated them.

1346
01:23:44,487 --> 01:23:46,189
One became passive,
the other aggressive.

1347
01:23:47,456 --> 01:23:49,258
So I took them
off the formula.

1348
01:23:49,292 --> 01:23:51,527
